{"tid":1698157,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"連仔/Admin 入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-11-07T10:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T05:29:36.000Z","uid":254456,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a254c78538b389633c3e19134b85221d9ad079a6","tid":1698157,"uid":254456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T10:00:01.000Z","msg":"連仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知你好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又要hold住個server<br />\n又要驚畀人ddos<br />\n不過希望你參考下呢度嘅意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 新增減去熱門分數的方法</span><br />\n我唔知道「拉」係唔係真係有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為唔係官方說明有呢個功能<br />\n如果冇用<br />\n我希望你新增呢個功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（因為據我所知，你瀏覽個post，都會對熱門分數有增加）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. 新增對會員<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n派膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/<br />\n賜酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>功能</span><br />\n如果我冇記錯<br />\n舊燈嗰個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">派膠/賜酒</span><br />\n係會影響到<span style=\"color: red;\">上熱門嘅機會</span><br />\n膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嘅數量越多 : 越難上熱門<br />\n酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嘅數量越多 : 較容易上熱門/對上熱門分數有加成<br />\netc.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3. 雙重驗證功能</span><br />\n呢樣冇乜可以講<br />\n連仔應該整緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最重要一樣 : FORCE LOGOUT</span><br />\n我唔知連仔仲有冇關注草泥馬（高登）嘅動向<br />\n事實上佢喺八月頭<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">曾經過force logout 過一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n而佢force logout 嘅方法係 : <br />\n<br />\n<em>首先下一至兩個星期之前出post通知會員<br />\n要求會員自己改密碼<br />\n去到一個限期前<br />\n佢都唔願意改密碼<br />\n先至強制force logout 呢一班人<br />\n而如果成功改密碼<br />\nSend一封電郵去佢嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">備用電郵<br />\n ( a.k.a.唔係isp嗰一個 ) </span><br />\n通知佢改咗新密碼<br />\n同時要求撳入個網址度<br />\n確認佢改咗新密碼</em><br />\n如此一來<br />\n就可以force logout 殭屍account/ 被盜用帳戶<br />\n又唔會對server造成太大負荷<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知道有啲point係比較難實行<br />\n但係我希望連仔可以盡做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗連仔都唔希望連登畀五毛入侵<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">認同請幫推</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b962b7e6911748b7d067f53d16ab1b04851ac8f3","tid":1698157,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:45:12.000Z","msg":"想問下樓主會對咩post用「拉」?其他台出嘅post?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02e39a0338dcc06e0703f40e9fa76c169898e770","tid":1698157,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:29:36.000Z","msg":"推"}]}